{"word":"G4783 - συγκατάθεσις - synkatáthesis - soong-kat-ath'-es-is - Agreement","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">συγκατάθεσις</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">synkatáthesis</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">soong-kat-ath'-es-is</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Agreement</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"சம்பந்தம் - பெயர்ச்சொல்."},{"paragraph":"a putting together or joint deposit approval, assent, agreement,"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G4784 - συγκατατίθεμαι - synkatatíthemai - soong-kat-at-ith'-em-ahee/4784\">G4784</a>; a <i>deposition</i> (of sentiment) in company <i>with</i>, that is, (figuratively) <i>accord</i> with: - agreement.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}